            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Complete o bloco de código para que esteja livre de erros de sintaxe.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"member = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Jason&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" member \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alexis&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;Jason&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Happy Birthday, &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + member)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"32\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"50\" /><option startIndex=\"54\" endIndex=\"59\" /><option startIndex=\"59\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option startIndex=\"87\" endIndex=\"88\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"member\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"for\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Happy Birthday, Jason\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>[</code> seguido de <code>]</code> e depois <code>print</code>, <code>(</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
