            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Por que o seguinte código gera um <code>IndexError</code>?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"scores = [\" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"180\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"scores[\" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Traceback (most recent call last):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"File &quot;script.py&quot;, line 2, in &lt;module&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    scores[5]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"IndexError: list index out of range\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">O índice está fora do intervalo</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>scores</code> não está definido</item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\"><code>scores</code> não é um dicionário</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">O índice está fora do intervalo.</p></body></html>"
