            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Escreva uma instrução que não resulte em um erro.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"team_a = \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"team_b = \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" team_a &gt; team_b:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Team A won the game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"33\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"null\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"false\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Team A won the game\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
