            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Que tipo de erro o seguinte código irá gerar?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"maximum = \" /><text value=\"30\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&quot;50&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" &lt; maximum: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;ok&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") \" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Traceback (most recent call last):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"File &quot;script.py&quot;, line 3, in &lt;module&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    if &quot;50&quot; &lt; maximum:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"TypeError: &quot;&lt;&quot; not supported between instances of &quot;str&quot; and &quot;int&quot;\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>TypeError</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>SyntaxError</code></item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\"><code>NameError</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>TypeError</code>.</p></body></html>"
