            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Onde no código a seguir o <code>SyntaxError</code> será identificado?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"guests = \" /><text value=\"24\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"table_size = \" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"tables_required = guests table_size\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(tables_required)\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"File &quot;script.py&quot;, line 3\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    tables_required = guests table_size\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"                             ^\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"SyntaxError: invalid syntax\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>tables_required = guests table_size</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>guests = 24</code></item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\"><code>print(tables_required)</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>tables_required = guests table_size</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: the `else` keyword",
            "id": 92548,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Imprima a mensagem apenas se o cálculo puder ser feito.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"total = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"people = \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"try\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\": \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" share = total / people\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"except\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"pass\" class=\"keyword\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your share is &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + str(share)+ \" /><text value=\"&quot; units.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"63\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option startIndex=\"69\" endIndex=\"73\" /><option startIndex=\"76\" endIndex=\"81\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"raise\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"finally\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Your share is 0.5 units.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>pass</code> seguido de <code>else</code> e finalmente <code>print</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
